Title: The Superalgebraic Approach to Supergravity
Authors: C.R. Preitschopf and M.A. Vasiliev
Comments: latex, talk given at the International Seminar on Supersymmetries and
  Quantum Symmetries, Dubna, Russia, July 22 - 26, 1997 and at the 31st
  International Symposium Ahrenshoop on the Theory of Elementary Particles,
  Buckow, September 2-6, 1997
Report-no: FIAN/TD/15-98, HUB EP-98/29
\\
  We formulate classical actions for N=1 supergravity in D=(1,3) as a gauge
theory of OSp(1|4). One may choose the action such that it does not include a
cosmological term.
